# Task T-007@20260416T043834Z: Add creative DSP and cross-modal feature publication.

## Acceptance Criteria

- DSP scene lab supports spectral freeze, smear, morph, convolution, delay, and physical-model gestures as named blocks<br/>- `/tmp/glyph_audio_features.json` or successor state includes brightness, motion, density, texture, salience, DSP blocks, and mapping hints<br/>- tests verify feature values correlate with known synthetic inputs

